10 An Act relating to controlled dangerous substances;
amending 63 O.S. 2021, Sections 2-204, as last
11 amended by Section 3, Chapter 308, O.S.L. 2024, and
2-210 (63 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 2-204), which
12 relate to the Uniform Controlled Dangerous Substances
Act; adding certain substances to Schedules I and IV;
13 amending 63 O.S. 2021, Section 2-309B, as amended by
Section 1, Chapter 69, O.S.L. 2022 (63 O.S. Supp.
14 2025, Section 2-309B), which relates to the Anti-Drug
Diversion Act; modifying scope of certain
15 definitions; and providing an effective date.
