14 specialty or field of health care, for a dispenser doing business in
15 a particular location, or for a recipient;
16 5. “Recipient” means the person for whom a prescription is
17 prescribed and who is the lawful intended ultimate user;
18 6. “Recipient’s agent” means a person who is authorized by the
19 ultimate user to pick up the recipient’s medication and deliver it
20 to the recipient or a person who claims a prescription other than
21 the person to whom the medication is prescribed;
